node.text: Take on the lethal and evolving Archaen threat in Rainbow Six Extraction. New gear, new abilities, new strategy. And if one of you goes down in the containment zone, it’s up to you and your teammates to mount a rescue and make sure everyone gets out alive. Who’s Got YouR6?
